data.name: TextBox3.Text
data.value: The XPS CP Sim defaults to port 8448, and requires elevated privileges to place an SSL certificate in the keystore for https communication. After starting the XPS CP Sim, configure the R1 XPS connector to point to this HOSTNAME:8448. The XPS CP Sim will accept any username/password combination as long as they are not the same.
